{
  "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "解线性方程组时，我们常用高斯消元把矩阵化成上三角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "可如果换一组右端项，又要重新消元一遍，实在浪费。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.59,
      "size": 41472,
      "text": "LU 分解的想法是：把消元的过程本身记录下来，一次分解，反复使用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "eliminate",
      "line_id": "elim-1",
      "filename": "eliminate-elim-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/eliminate-elim-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "我们对矩阵 A 做高斯消元，逐列把主元下方的元素清成零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "eliminate",
      "line_id": "elim-2",
      "filename": "eliminate-elim-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/eliminate-elim-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "消元结束，A 就变成了一个上三角矩阵，我们把它叫做 U。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "eliminate",
      "line_id": "elim-3",
      "filename": "eliminate-elim-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/eliminate-elim-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "每一步只用主元行去减下面的行，规则非常规整。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "store",
      "line_id": "store-1",
      "filename": "store-store-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/store-store-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "关键在于：每次消元用到的那个乘数，不要丢掉。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "store",
      "line_id": "store-2",
      "filename": "store-store-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/store-store-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "把乘数填到一个对角线为一的下三角矩阵里，这就是 L。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "store",
      "line_id": "store-3",
      "filename": "store-store-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/store-store-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "L 就像一本账本，忠实记下了每一步是怎么消元的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "verify",
      "line_id": "verify-1",
      "filename": "verify-verify-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/verify-verify-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "神奇的是，把 L 和 U 乘起来，正好还原出原矩阵 A。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "verify",
      "line_id": "verify-2",
      "filename": "verify-verify-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/verify-verify-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.6,
      "size": 41616,
      "text": "有了 A 等于 L 乘 U，解方程就拆成两个三角方程：先前代，再回代。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "逐步查看消元过程，看每一步是如何把一个元素清成零的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "LU 分解把矩阵拆成下三角 L 与上三角 U 的乘积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "一次分解，就能高效应对同一系数、不同右端的多个方程组。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "lu-decomposition",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/lu-decomposition/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "把消元过程记成账本，这就是 LU 分解的智慧，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
